Package: ancombcVizhelper
Type: Package
Title: Tidy and Visualize Results from ANCOM-BC2
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person(
        given = "So-Yeon",
        family = "Kim",
        role = c("aut", "cre"),
        email = "kim.soyeon.bio@gmail.com"
    )
Description: Provides tools to tidy, summarize, and visualize differential
    abundance results generated by ANCOM-BC2. The package converts ANCOM-BC2
    model output into a standardized tidy format and generates customizable,
    publication-ready visualizations, including log-fold change plots,
    heatmaps, and comparison-specific summaries.
